=> Vector Search Documentation

1. Vector Database

We use FAISS:
IndexFlatL2
Distance Metric:
L2 (Euclidean distance)


2. Embedding Model

Model: all-MiniLM-L6-v2  
Dimension: 384  
Advantages:
i) Lightweight
ii) Fast
iii) Good semantic performance


3. Storage Structure

Each entry contains:
{
    embedding: [384-dim vector],
    metadata: {
        user_id,
        type,
        date,
        preference_text
    }
}


4. Retrieval Strategy

i) Convert query to embedding
ii) Perform top-k search
iii) Filter by user_id
iv) Extract relevant metadata


5. Time Complexity

Search: O(n) for flat index  
Memory: O(n Ã— d)
